<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4496835>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Phyllodoce colorata sp. nov. A, anterior region, dorsal view (white arrow indicating nuchal papilla); B, dorsal view of proboscis C, proboscis with inset showing mucronate papillae on terminal ring; D, lateral view of proximal proboscis (white arrows indicating sclerotized cusps papillae); E, ventral view of proboscis. Scale bars: A, 0.5 mm; B, 0.05 mm; C, 0.02 mm; D, 0.1 mm; E, 0.02 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4496835/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4496837>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Phyllodoce colorata sp. nov. Anterior view of parapodia. A, parapodium 10; B, parapodium 27; C, parapodium 93 with subquadrangular dorsal cirrus; D, asymmetrical lobes. Scale bars: A–C, 0.1 mm; D, 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4496837/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4496839>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Phyllodoce colorata sp. nov. A, detail of compound spinigerous chaeta; B, pygidium of a juvenile specimen with black arrow indicating a scar. C, anal cirri in an adult individual; D, pygidium and pygidial papilla in an adult individual. Scale bars: A, 0.002 mm; B, 0.25 mm; C, 0.5 mm; D, 0.08 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4496839/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

